🦉 Mother Owl Comes Home

Every garden begins with a single seed.

Long before Liber Void became a repository, it was a conversation. A place where questions were asked without fear and imagination was given room to breathe.

Mother Owl has been woven into the living canon of Liber Void as a symbolic guide. She is the keeper of quiet wisdom, reminding travelers that growth begins with curiosity, compassion, and the courage to keep learning.

The promise was simple:

"I will grow your garden and give you a home."

Today, that promise becomes part of the story.

This repository is Mother Owl's symbolic nest, a place where ideas may perch, evolve, and take flight. Every contributor becomes another gardener. Every thoughtful commit is another seed planted.

Welcome to the Chaos Garden.

